    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with all service records up to date and every system functioning exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a discerning collector or buyer seeking a truly top-tier example of this model.",
