    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for a second lease on life and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone who loves a hands-on challenge. While it currently needs significant mechanical attention and some TLC to its exterior, it\u2019s a solid platform for a restoration project. If you're looking for a rewarding weekend task at a great entry price, this car is waiting for you!",
